 be’). This has been one of the most enduringly popular girls' names."],"variants":[{"name":"Sara","meanings":["Variant of   Sarah .  This is the form used in the Greek of the New Testament (Hebrews 11:11)."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Sarah de Bedford was born about 1280, in Moyne, County Tipperary, Ireland. She married Ulphram Wolfram II Berneval before 1300, in Ireland. They were the parents of at least 2 sons."},"et":{"about 1300–":"umbes 1280–Surnud","1280–Male":"1280–Surnud","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","1310–1374":"1310–1374","1280–Female":"1280–Surnud","before 1300":"enne 1300","1300":"1300","1310":"1310","1374":"1374","about 1300":"umbes 1280","1280":"1280","Ireland":"Iirimaa","Crickstown, Meath, Ireland":"Crickstown, County Meath, Iirimaa","Drimnagh, Dublin, Ireland":"Drimnagh, County Dublin, Iirimaa","Moyne, County Tipperary, Ireland":"Moyne, County Tipperary, Iirimaa"},"fi":{"about 1300–":"noin 1280–Kuollut","1280–Male":"1280–Kuollut","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","1310–1374":"1310–1374","1280–Female":"1280–Kuollut","before 1300":"ennen vuotta 1300","1300":"1300","1310":"1310","1374":"1374","about 1300":"noin 1280","1280":"1280","Ireland":"Irlanti","Crickstown, Meath, Ireland":"Crickstown, County Meath, Irlanti","Drimnagh, Dublin, Ireland":"Drimnagh, County Dublin, Irlanti","Moyne, County Tipperary, Ireland":"Moyne, County Tipperary, Irlanti"},"fr":{"about 1300–":"environ 1280–Décédée","1280–Male":"1280–Décédé","1300–Male":"1300–Décédé","1310–1374":"1310–1374","1280–Female":"1280–Décédée","before 1300":"avant 1300","1300":"1300","1310":"1310","1374":"1374","about 1300":"environ 1280","1280":"1280","Ireland":"Irlande","Crickstown, Meath, Ireland":"Crickstown, County Meath, Irlande","Drimnagh, Dublin, Ireland":"Drimnagh, County Dublin, Irlande","Moyne, County Tipperary, Ireland":"Moyne, County Tipperary, Irlande","lifeSummary":"Sarah de Bedford est née environ 1280, à Moyne, County Tipperary, Irlande. Elle a épousé Ulphram Wolfram II Berneval avant 1300, à Irlande. Ils 